S.A. Dubrovnaja
Tatar State Pedagogical and Humanitarian University, Kazan
Strategy of behaviour Hypericum perforatum (L.) is defined by feature of formation of
system of runaways which develop from the additional kidneys located in the basis of
elevated runaway.
